# Skill Registry R0.1
# Adarian 系统已注册 skill 能力清单。
# 每个条目对应一个 Hermes skill（~/.hermes/skills/）或 CC Switch skill（~/.cc-switch/skills/）。

## Hermes Skills

### Category: autonomous-ai-agents

- id: skill-claude-code
  name: Claude Code
  type: skill
  status: active
  purpose: 委派编码任务给 Claude Code CLI（特性开发、PR、审查）
  applicable_lanes: [A_LINE_FORMAL, B_LINE_LIGHTWEIGHT_DAG, WORKYB_RUNTIME, DOGFOOD_TEST]
  inputs: [task prompt, working directory]
  outputs: [code changes, PR, review report]
  allowed_paths: ["~/项目开发/**"]
  forbidden_paths: ["~/.hermes/**", "~/.cc-switch/**"]
  tools_required: [claude]
  permission_level: write_within_scope
  risk_level: medium
  owner_approval_required: false
  validation: [exit code 0, expected outputs exist]
  return_format: RunResult
  evidence_paths: [task_dir/runtime/result.json, task_dir/logs/stdout.log]
  depends_on: [executor-claude]

- id: skill-codex
  name: Codex CLI
  type: skill
  status: active
  purpose: 委派编码任务给 OpenAI Codex CLI（特性开发、重构、批处理修复）
  applicable_lanes: [A_LINE_FORMAL, B_LINE_LIGHTWEIGHT_DAG, WORKYB_RUNTIME, DOGFOOD_TEST]
  inputs: [task prompt, working directory]
  outputs: [code changes, JSONL events]
  allowed_paths: ["~/项目开发/**"]
  forbidden_paths: ["~/.hermes/**", "~/.cc-switch/**"]
  tools_required: [codex]
  permission_level: write_within_scope
  risk_level: medium
  owner_approval_required: false
  validation: [exit code 0, JSONL valid, expected outputs exist]
  return_format: JSONL
  evidence_paths: [task_dir/runtime/result.json, task_dir/logs/stdout.log]
  depends_on: [executor-codex]

### Category: pm-runtime (13 skills)

- id: skill-pm-runtime
  name: PM Runtime Index
  type: skill
  status: active
  purpose: 中台运行索引 — PM Runtime 岗位说明书入口。加载后按图索骥，指引业务方加载对应子技能。
  applicable_lanes: [WORKYB_RUNTIME, DOGFOOD_TEST]
  inputs: [runtime task dispatch request]
  outputs: [sub-skill routing guidance]
  allowed_paths: ["~/.hermes/**", "~/项目开发/AdarianMigration/adarian mvp/**"]
  forbidden_paths: []
  tools_required: [hermes]
  permission_level: readonly
  risk_level: low
  owner_approval_required: false
  validation: [skill loadable]

- id: skill-pm-relay
  name: PM Relay — 中台派发引擎
  type: skill
  status: active
  purpose: Relay Runner 执行器架构、双执行器模式（Claude tmux / Codex tmux）、dispatch 流程、CC Switch 路由、observer 模式、超时策略、完成检测原则、心跳监视器
  depends_on: [skill-pm-relay-dialog, skill-relay-skill-governance]
  applicable_lanes: [WORKYB_RUNTIME, DOGFOOD_TEST, A_LINE_FORMAL]
  inputs: [task_config.yaml, prompt.md]
  outputs: [dispatch plan, executor routing]
  allowed_paths: ["~/.hermes/**", "~/项目开发/AdarianMigration/adarian mvp/**"]
  forbidden_paths: []
  tools_required: [relay_runner]
  permission_level: write_within_scope
  risk_level: medium
  owner_approval_required: false
  validation: [dispatch completes]

- id: skill-pm-relay-dialog
  name: PM Relay Dialog — 对话框处理规约
  type: skill
  status: active
  purpose: dialog_watcher 主批、DialogHandler fallback、auto-mode、多弹窗处理、权限弹窗协议
